Hardware System Engineer (IBM, HP, SUN)
Responsibilities
The main responsibility of this position is to manage the infrastructure system.Server management is a primary responsibility, specially for :installing, maintaining and upgrading serversAlso  responsible for ensuring the servers are backed up, performance and availability are monitored, and that the server data is secure from unauthorized access Requirement:  Bachelor Degree (S1) from reputable university, major in Information Technology / ScienceHaving an experience of Hardware and Software installation for Blade and Storage ServerHaving an experience of Unix System’s implementation and administration (solaris, linux) for SUN engineerHaving related certificate will be an advantageTypically more than 3 years of relevant experienceCan Communicate in English (written & verbal)If you meet the above requirement, please submit your application to nana.widiana@s-net.co.id or by using APPLY NOWOnly short listed candidates will be notified.
